<item>
            <title>[LU-15559] add do_node_vp and do_facet_vp</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15559</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Using do_node() and do_facet() sometimes requires elaborate escaping of commands lines. It is often the case that these escaped command lines behave differently when executed on local or remote nodes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So let&apos;s add new TF functions do_node_vp() and do_facet_vp() that handle the escaping for us and work the same way on local or remote nodes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
